&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Step into Your Future with Advanced Urology Centers of New York!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The&lt;strong&gt; Bronx Clinic&lt;/strong&gt; of &lt;strong&gt;Advanced Urology Centers of New York &lt;/strong&gt;is growing, and we&#39;re on the hunt for a &lt;strong&gt;Nurse Practitioner &lt;/strong&gt;or &lt;strong&gt;Physician Assistant &lt;/strong&gt;to join our team in&lt;strong&gt; 2026.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Bronx Clinic, situated in the heart of NYC’s greenest borough—where the culture is rich, and the pizza is iconic.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work Model:&lt;/strong&gt; Outpatient-focused—no hospital rounds, no weekend marathons!&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt; Flexible Monday through Friday, with no on-call shifts. Yes, you read that right: no midnight alarms.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation:&lt;/strong&gt; Competitive guaranteed salary plus a work RVU bonus model. Hard work pays—literally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why the Bronx?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Life in the Bronx is about more than just the Yankees and the Zoo. Here’s what makes this borough a perfect place to call home:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Housing:&lt;/strong&gt; From historic Art Deco apartments along the Grand Concourse to the charming seaside vibes of City Island, there’s a home for every lifestyle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Diverse Community:&lt;/strong&gt; The Bronx is a true melting pot—diverse, vibrant, and full of energy. You’ll find a global community that brings an unmatched depth of culture and flavor to daily life.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Getting Around:&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;By car:&lt;/strong&gt; Easily access the Major Deegan, the Cross Bronx, or the Henry Hudson Parkway.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;By rail:&lt;/strong&gt; Catch the 1, 2, 4, 5, 6, B, or D trains and be in Midtown Manhattan in a New York minute.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education Excellence:&lt;/strong&gt; Home to prestigious institutions like Fordham University and Manhattan College, providing plenty of opportunities to keep your brainpower sharp.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Play Where You Stay!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Outdoor Fun:&lt;/strong&gt; With over 25% of the borough dedicated to parkland, you can explore Pelham Bay Park (NYC&#39;s largest!) or the stunning New York Botanical Garden.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Culture &amp;amp; Entertainment:&lt;/strong&gt; Visit the world-famous Bronx Zoo or catch a game at Yankee Stadium. For artsy vibes, the Bronx Museum of the Arts is a must-see.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shopping &amp;amp; Dining:&lt;/strong&gt; From the &quot;real&quot; Little Italy on Arthur Avenue to the shops at Bay Plaza, the food and retail scene is legendary. Think authentic pasta, fresh seafood at City Island, and hidden gems on every corner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Community Perks&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Bronx is big on neighborhood pride and community spirit. Street festivals, local farmers&#39; markets, and vibrant community gardens give you endless ways to connect with your neighbors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Safety First&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;With dedicated local precincts and world-class medical facilities, the Bronx is committed to keeping its residents safe and healthy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Patients Come First.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Every decision we make is anchored in strengthening patient care. Our physicians lead with a commitment to quality, access, and outcomes, and our shared infrastructure ensures they have the tools, data, and support to continually elevate care in every community we serve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Physician-Led Organization at Every Level.&lt;/strong&gt;

