&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Parks, Trails &amp;amp; Outdoor Fun:&lt;/strong&gt; From the scenic trails at Skokie Northshore Sculpture Park to dozens of neighborhood parks and recreational facilities, there are plenty of opportunities to stay active and enjoy the outdoors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shopping &amp;amp; Entertainment Close to Home:&lt;/strong&gt; Whether you&#39;re catching a movie, exploring local businesses, or shopping at Westfield Old Orchard, Skokie offers conveniences typically found in much larger communities.&l

