&lt;p&gt;Are you a &lt;strong&gt;Nurse Practitioner (NP)&lt;/strong&gt; or &lt;strong&gt;Physician Assistant (PA) &lt;/strong&gt;ready to grow your career in a thriving, patient-focused practice? &lt;strong&gt;AUA’s&lt;/strong&gt; busy &lt;strong&gt;Joliet Clinic&lt;/strong&gt;—located in the heart of &lt;strong&gt;Chicago’s southwest suburbs &lt;/strong&gt;is expanding!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why You’ll Love Working with AUA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Find Your Balance:&lt;/strong&gt; Enjoy a &lt;strong&gt;Monday–Friday&lt;/strong&gt; schedule!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Outpatient-Centered Practice:&lt;/strong&gt; Deliver outstanding care in a supportive environment focused on follow-ups and new patient consults.&lt;/li&gt;
