&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborative Team Culture:&lt;/strong&gt; Join a team of &lt;strong&gt;8 full-time physicians and 3 experienced APPs&lt;/strong&gt; who believe in shared knowledge and seamless patient care.&lt;/li&gt;
